        <heading>Section </heading>
        <content>
          <p>CHAPTER 3.  LOAN ON INTEREST
Art. 2913.  Payment of interest presumed in release of principal
When the principal of the loan is released without reservation as to interest, it is presumed that the interest is also released.</p>
        </content>
